{"data":[{"text":"終わりそうです。 https://t.co/mpxrHTfzEu","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":196},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037480381403062289"],"created_at":"2026-03-27T10:42:32.000Z","id":"2037480381403062289","entities":{"urls":[{"start":9,"end":32,"url":"https://t.co/mpxrHTfzEu","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/miyabi_foxx/status/2035669473844404514","display_url":"x.com/miyabi_foxx/st…"}]},"author_id":"1809220419691675648"},{"text":"AIで上手に仕事する方法はいくつもありますが結局は、\n\n①実際作業やらせる\n②ミス発見する\n③チェックリストに起こす\n④AIに毎回③を確認させて作業させる\n⑤以下ループで強化\n\nが原則です。最初から最強のプロンプトとskillも作れない認識でいるべき。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":4,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":1,"impression_count":243},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036822844492198128"],"created_at":"2026-03-25T15:09:43.000Z","id":"2036822844492198128","author_id":"1809220419691675648"},{"text":"computer useで過去のスタエフ音声をnoteに移行してもらってますが、荒削りなものの指示出し徹底すればかなり精度高そう。\n\n人間がやったら7〜8時間くらいかかる作業なのですが、私が寝ている間、会議してる間に進めてくれるの幸福度高い。 https://t.co/EPH3NrAmB0","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":3,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":1,"impression_count":381},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036666099828494644"],"created_at":"2026-03-25T04:46:52.000Z","id":"2036666099828494644","entities":{"urls":[{"start":122,"end":145,"url":"https://t.co/EPH3NrAmB0","expanded_url":"https://x.com/miyabi_foxx/status/2036666099828494644/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/EPH3NrAmB0","media_key":"3_2036665725751111680"}]},"author_id":"1809220419691675648"},{"text":"あと「枝葉」を追う時間は無駄中の無駄でしかありません。\n\n・現場で使えないAIツール\n・中途半端な機能\n・Claudeで代替できる内容\n\nこれらは全部枝葉です。\n今触る必要は0だと思います。 https://t.co/L8Kv3kqbwD","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":7,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":2,"impression_count":612},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036465961923174448"],"created_at":"2026-03-24T15:31:35.000Z","id":"2036465961923174448","entities":{"urls":[{"start":96,"end":119,"url":"https://t.co/L8Kv3kqbwD","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/miyabi_foxx/status/2036463968261488870","display_url":"x.com/miyabi_foxx/st…"}]},"author_id":"1809220419691675648"},{"text":"1つ大きな決断。\n\nみやびはClaudeと心中することにしました。\n\n私はもうClaude以外のAIツールはすべて「枝葉」だと断言します。\n\n実際2024年からメインで使ってきました。途中でChatGPTやGeminiなどがトップに君臨した期間はありましたが、結局Claudeが返り咲きを繰り返し、この2026年3月で完全にAI","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":28,"quote_count":1,"bookmark_count":5,"impression_count":2131},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036463968261488870"],"created_at":"2026-03-24T15:23:40.000Z","id":"2036463968261488870","author_id":"1809220419691675648"},{"text":"Claudeブラウザ操作（computer use）の設定方法置いておきます。 https://t.co/1gutwJqBOA","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":1,"reply_count":1,"like_count":15,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":5,"impression_count":782},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036320690270511304","2036320845367566468"],"created_at":"2026-03-24T05:54:57.000Z","id":"2036320845367566468","entities":{"urls":[{"start":40,"end":63,"url":"https://t.co/1gutwJqBOA","expanded_url":"https://x.com/miyabi_foxx/status/2036320845367566468/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/1gutwJqBOA","media_key":"3_2036320578311954436"},{"start":40,"end":63,"url":"https://t.co/1gutwJqBOA","expanded_url":"https://x.com/miyabi_foxx/status/2036320845367566468/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/1gutwJqBOA","media_key":"3_2036320578290982921"}]},"author_id":"1809220419691675648"},{"text":"Claudeブラウザ操作の設定方法置いておきます。 https://t.co/gUkUVazFIG","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":10},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036320690270511304","2036320845367566468"],"created_at":"2026-03-24T05:54:20.000Z","id":"2036320690270511304","entities":{"urls":[{"start":26,"end":49,"url":"https://t.co/gUkUVazFIG","expanded_url":"https://x.com/miyabi_foxx/status/2036320690270511304/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/gUkUVazFIG","media_key":"3